    "description": "We at Max Healthcare International Enterprises are looking for an experienced Consultant Physician based out of Mysuru. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Max Healthcare International Enterprises:\nMax Healthcare International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Max Healthcare International Enterprises!",
